snippet.title: Ultracore - Available for Pre-Order Now!
snippet.description:
PRE-ORDER NOW: https://store.strictlylimitedgames.com/pages/buy-ultracore

After 25 years , its about time to get HARDCORE!
A mystery in video game history and in the legacy of DICE is about to be solved.

Coming to Nintendo Switch, PS4 and PS Vita SOON!
ULTRACORE Physical Edition is strictly limited and only available until 30th June! 
Make sure to get your copy while it lasts.

https://ultracore.strictlylimitedgames.com/
https://www.strictlylimitedgames.com/
FB: https://www.facebook.com/StrictlyLTDG...
Twitter: https://twitter.com/RealStrictlyLTD/

Music: MEGA DRIVE - Activate Your Steel
Trailer: Marcel Gülzow / Commander Marcel (https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCcZ-MWYLbg3do065IY_YJ9A)
